title: Add a Column With a Default Value in Mysql
tags: @zettel _method mysql
roam-id: 4b3c60e1-b770-4d2e-a2d6-df572fdbbc6f
type: text/markdown

``` sql
ALTER TABLE table_name ADD COLUMN column_name data_type DEFAULT default_value;
```

full example:

``` sql
ALTER TABLE bulk_coin_charging ADD COLUMN coin_completion_enabled bit(1) DEFAULT b'0';
```
